<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>Ann Morgan</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/2382?language=en' lang='en'>
My year reading a book from every country in the world
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
